{
  "texts": [
    "However, the findings of this study indicate that although chatbot technology can generate meaningful conversations, there are still numerous challenges to address in order to guarantee its successful implementation in such urban design projects.",
    "In chatbot prompt design, we face a unique challenge that stems not only from the unpredictable nature of LLMs but also from the variability of human behavior.",
    "Previous chatbot research has compared the unpredictability of LLMs to \"herding AI cats\" due to the tendency of LLMs to generate unexpected responses (Zamfirescu-Pereira et al., 2023).",
    "This metaphor is particularly pertinent when designing an assistant chatbot.",
    "However, our chatbot's primary aim is significantly differentto extract specific information from human users."
  ]
}